snippet.title: Anode Gameplay Trailer | Kittehface Software Steam Trailer
snippet.description:
"Anode reintroduces the classic falling-block puzzle genre, with new twists and challenges! Link blocks back and forth across each other. Match angled couplers to create chains of multiple colors. Play Mission Mode and complete randomly-generated objectives for more challenge!" - Kittehface Software

Game: https://store.steampowered.com/app/401120/Anode/
